1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:05,805
You can't show up to a dirt bike event you never discover, and honestly, that's what I felt as a new rider.
你无法参加一场你从未发现的越野摩托活动，说实话，这就是我当年作为新手车友的感受。

2
00:00:05,805 --> 00:00:11,610
If you don't already know the track name, follow the right Instagram page, or know somebody who's plugged in,
如果你本来就不知道赛道名字，没有关注对的 Instagram 主页，也不认识圈内的熟人，

3
00:00:11,610 --> 00:00:15,480
you might just never find out there's a ride day happening right next to you.
你可能永远不会发现，就在你旁边正在举行一场骑行日活动。

4
00:00:15,508 --> 00:00:18,329
And that's one of the reasons why I'm building DirtBikeX.
这也正是我打造 DirtBikeX 的原因之一。

5
00:00:18,329 --> 00:00:23,030
I want tracks to be easier to find, and exactly where riders are looking.
我希望赛道更容易被找到，而且就出现在车友们正在寻找的地方。

6
00:00:23,030 --> 00:00:28,670
Here, if you run a dirt bike track, you can get verified as a track owner so riders know your updates are real.
在这里，如果你经营一条越野摩托赛道，你可以认证成为赛道主，让车友知道你发布的更新是真实的。

7
00:00:28,950 --> 00:00:34,010
You can create ride days, races, open practices, and even reoccurring events.
你可以创建骑行日、比赛、自由练习，甚至是重复举办的活动。

8
00:00:34,010 --> 00:00:41,980
Then, fellow riders can find them in the Events tab, filter what's nearby, RSVP, and get reminded before it starts.
然后，其他车友可以在「活动」标签页里找到它们，筛选附近的活动，报名参加，并在开始前收到提醒。

9
00:00:41,980 --> 00:00:47,795
The idea is simple, help riders find places to ride, and help tracks to get more people to show up.
想法很简单，帮助车友找到骑行的地方，也帮助赛道吸引更多人到场。

10
00:00:47,795 --> 00:00:53,610
My name is Rubio, and if you're a track owner, comment "OWNER" and I'll send you the link!
我叫鲁比奥，如果你是赛道主，评论「OWNER」，我就把链接发给你！
